Headers:
Copy src/ndofdev_external.h to release\libraries\include\ndofdev_external.h

Windows:
Open the project.
Build Debug and Release.
Copy src\win_project_files\Debug\libndofdev.lib to release\libraries\i686-win32\lib_debug
Copy src\win_project_files\Release\libndofdev.lib to release\libraries\i686-win32\lib_release

XCode:
Open the project.
Build Debug and Release.
Copy src/build/Debug/libndofdev.dylib to release/libraries/universal-darwin/lib_debug/
Copy src/build/Release/libndofdev.dylib to release/libraries/universal-darwin/lib_release/


Linux:
No official Linux support is maintained in this library.
A drop-in replacement for Linux is maintained by Jan Ciger at: http://www.aaue.dk/~janoc/index.php?n=Personal.3DConnexionSpaceNavigatorSupport#secondlife

